Installation
---------------------------------------------------------------------
To install apertium-tagger-training-tools you need to have installed
the following packages:

libxml2, at least version 2.6.17 
lttoolbox, at least version 3.0.0
apertium, at least version 3.0.0

Once you have all the required software installed, install
apertium-tagger-training-tools in the common way:

$ ./configure && make

and as a root

# make install

Good luck!

